<font face="Verdana" size="6" color="#0000FF">What are the components of COM+? </font>
<a href="p7.htm"><img border="0" src="next.gif" width="26" height="26"></a></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">1) A runtime or execution environment<br>
</font></p>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">2) Extensible services, which are provided by 
Microsoft, which include transactions, security, real enough time, load 
balancing, and automatic memory management. Additional extensible services will 
be provided by third party developers</font></p>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5"><br>
<font color="#FF0000">3) Innovation, with key concepts such as Interception, which enables many of the 
extensible services which COM+ provides</font></font></p>
